<p>作者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6331978); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6331978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610119495" alt="carter lu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6331978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6331978); return false;">carter lu</a></span>，作者页在<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/carter">此</a></p>
<p>心血来潮之作</p>
